name: POLARBEAR FANZINE ISSUE 1
description: Issue One of new fanzine Polarbear, featuring an exclusive interview with Namalee – - lead singer of Namalee n the Namazonz and co-creator of cult SuperSuper Magazine. also interviewed are hip musician Unicorn Kid with some of his artwork; DIY Culture fashionista, Ellie Rivers. then there’s reviews, articles, fashion, loadsa stuff !!! OUT NOW. 14/02/08
